108
00:11:44,310 --> 00:11:46,740
But if you want to win,
I can help you with that.

109
00:11:47,910 --> 00:11:51,140
I'll give you my contact if you're in.

110
00:11:51,690 --> 00:11:53,140
Or just give me your number.

111
00:11:53,180 --> 00:11:54,280
